The evidence with the title 'Here's the secret payoff to health insurance CEOs buried in the GOP ... ' says Mar 7, 2017  ... Here 's one crying out for exposure: The bill encourages health insurance companies to pay their top executives more . It does so by removing the ACA's limit on corporate tax deductions for executive pay . The cost to the American taxpayer of eliminating this provision : well in excess of $70 million a year. 
